msgctxt "talk06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh! <2.pa>You! <3.pa>Hi!\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>It's me! <5.pa>I'm the one <6.se_co>Prince Sidon<7.re_co> left at\n"
"the top of the tower! The name's Gruve!\n"
"\n"
"<8.so>In the end, I wasn't able to join up with\n"
"<9.se_co>Prince Sidon<10.re_co>..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: pause (short)
#. 5: sound
#. 6: pause (short)
#. 7: pause (short)
#. 8: single_choice
msgctxt "talk07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Instead, I worked up some fighting spirit\n"
"and jumped into <2.se_co>Zora River<3.re_co> from the top\n"
"of the tower.<4.pa> Then I came back here.\n"
"<5.so>I was...<6.pa>deeply moved seeing my\n"
"reflection on the water's surface\n"
"as I dove in... <7.pa>Yes. Deeply moved.<8.si_ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (short)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: set_colour (red)
#. 6: reset_colour
#. 7: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I don't expect you to understand this...<2.pa>\n"
"but one's diving form is their truest and\n"
"most beautiful form... <3.pa>Yes, truly.\n"
"So lately, I've been spending my days\n"
"scouting out diving spots.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>When you learn how to <5.se_co>climb waterfalls<6.re_co>,<7.pa>\n"
"please show me your beautiful form."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "talk09"
msgid "<1.so>Do you need something?<2.ra>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: sound
#. 4: set_colour (red)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk10"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Equipped like a normal Hylian, <2.pa>you can't\n"
"experience the joy of climbing waterfalls.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>But with the <4.se_co>Zora armor <5.re_co>that our\n"
"princesses are known to make...<6.pa>\n"
"Well, that's a completely different story."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: raw
msgctxt "talk11"
msgid "<1.so>Is there anything else you'd like to ask?<2.ra>"
msgstr ""

