msgctxt "talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>My favorite diving spot of late<2.pa> is\n"
"<3.se_co>Shatterback Point<4.re_co> at the tip of\n"
"<5.se_co>Ploymus Mountain<6.re_co>.\n"
"I can scarcely put it into words...<7.pa>the joy\n"
"of your own reflection when diving into\n"
"<8.se_co>East Reservoir Lake<9.re_co> from there...\n"
"<10.so>However, a <11.se_co>Lynel<12.re_co> does reside on\n"
"<13.se_co>Ploymus Mountain<14.re_co>.<15.pa> If you go,\n"
"be prepared for the worst."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "talk14"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I'm constantly finding more and more\n"
"diving spots to show off the beautiful\n"
"diving form.\n"
"<2.so>If you can climb waterfalls too,<3.pa> I'd like to\n"
"challenge you to dive from as many\n"
"different waterfalls as you can!"
msgstr ""

