msgctxt "talk16"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Sorry I didn't introduce myself sooner.<2.pa>\n"
"I'm Gruve.\n"
"\n"
"I used to help <3.se_co>Prince Sidon<4.re_co> with his\n"
"search for a Hylian.\n"
"\n"
"<5.so>For you to find him yourself is\n"
"a godsend!<6.pa> Yes, it is!\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>However, while searching for a Hylian,\n"
"<8.se_co>Prince Sidon<9.re_co> left me stranded on\n"
"a tower..."
msgstr ""

